:3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b46c19e54685165b7a658e62f9c404e7b4998a41","tid":2183424,"uid":5129,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"70372475f12396327af24073808146ab8d119b25","tid":2183424,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:31:49.000Z","msg":"嘩 屌你老母 個陣人情味重撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:36:02.000Z","msg":"當年仲笑鳩皇馬炒C朗冇人情味<br />\n<br />\n估唔到而家回力鏢咁撚快<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T06:32:01.000Z","msg":"C朗個次已經叫做兩邊盡量做得好好睇睇 <br />\n雖然大家都知兩邊因為人工同續約問題有矛盾 但起碼叫做各自都無公開內情<br />\n最後出黎結果係C朗話自己主動離隊 皇馬唔會阻止阿朗 放佢去想去既祖記 收筆唔算高既轉會費（當時阿朗份違約其實成10億）出篇感激文道別<br />\n<br />\n雖然無搞咩排場 唔算風光 但相比起依家美斯同巴塞 <br />\n已經起碼唔算難睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83a56b414988cd6475cf66033883a961df9915ae","tid":2183424,"uid":36049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T06:34:49.000Z","msg":"疤狗肉酸到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d3fb2a3950e09e3afa4d78d5a1fa4d0fe64243","tid":2183424,"uid":127299,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f8e7f0a6c2e08a35a8bff7627e24d279158185e","tid":2183424,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T02:39:27.000Z","msg":"據西班牙媒體稱，美斯和巴塞的戰爭面臨升級，球會正在考慮對阿根廷人處以重罰。<br />\n<br />\n  美斯沒有參加巴塞球會的新冠病毒檢測，接著又缺席了週一的訓練。《馬卡報》稱，巴塞考慮對美斯處以重罰。<br />\n<br />\n  根據西甲各球會、西甲聯盟與西班牙足協的共同協議，如果一名球員無故「曠工」達到三次，球會將有權對他進行重罰，包括扣除11天工資，或者罰款月薪的25%。美斯的「曠工」情況已有兩次（缺席檢測以及週一的訓練），再有一次缺訓，將觸及這一處罰規定。<br />\n<br />\n  不過，美斯方面並不認為自己違紀，他認為自己已經跳出合約，不再是巴塞球員。而巴塞方面在考慮處罰時，也會謹小慎微，希望留有餘地，但如果美斯繼續「罷工」，不排除球會真的下重手處罰美斯的可能。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T06:34:57.000Z","msg":"佢唔踢係無錯呀，<br />\n球會又話6月已經完約，重踢乜鬼？"},{"pid":"4eb4f411ac2e629e64ea27b7f24adc973b8c6cad","tid":2183424,"uid":78905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fe8488784dfbe5dfcb43c2584a88b8746712d32c","tid":2183424,"uid":53990,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:04:01.000Z","msg":"2大球王都走得咁肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T06:35:45.000Z","msg":"牙朗算係咁啦"},{"pid":"1d30eb0efe5db08b3ac6a0e3e33804ff693ad711","tid":2183424,"uid":127233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T06:44:26.000Z","msg":"西甲真係好撚低賤,想走既唔比走,唔想走既就比人迫走"},{"pid":"5ffabaf54adfcd5b0535bb27151b0434b5a33138","tid":2183424,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b729381c8da47b0ea9fd79a5865d9bada590b7d3","tid":2183424,"uid":33885,"like":60,"dislike":5,"score":55,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T02:57:29.000Z","msg":"On撚9垃圾管理層<br />\n美斯為個球隊貢獻咗幾撚多呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T06:47:12.000Z","msg":"唔知道 睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"132a08d71e0a82bf163bc4a4e02a5f18f8cd126f","tid":2183424,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"181c21d6829d08e155015b5328efce9f2a94fdb5","tid":2183424,"uid":14652,"like":102,"dislike":3,"score":99,"quote":{"pid":"b1c430ddcc34adbbccd3f5610840dd7c03d19161","tid":2183424,"uid":23833,"like":114,"dislike":3,"score":111,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T02:54:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T02:57:12.000Z","msg":"疤真係最低賤球會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T06:49:25.000Z","msg":"罷睇閪球會"},{"pid":"0a9604e6ea42c630257fa09d1dc56d1fa4462d15","tid":2183424,"uid":54431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45f94bc17f9d6597fa8558f214beb0022a314336","tid